params._owner: An address for whom to query the balance

returns._0: The number of NFTs owned by `_owner`, possibly zero

ownerOf(uint256).details: NFTs assigned to zero address are considered invalid, and queries  about them do throw.

returns._0: The address of the owner of the NFT

supportsInterface(bytes4).details: Interface identification is specified in ERC-165. This uses less than 30.000 gas.

params.interfaceID: The interface identifier, as specified in ERC-165

returns._0: A count of valid NFTs tracked by this contract, where each one of  them has an assigned and queryable owner not equal to the zero address

params._from: The current owner of the NFT
